title: How much do tube drivers get paid, and why are they striking now?
text: Road and rail transport How much do tube drivers get paid, and why are they striking now? Tube strikes are back as unions still aren't happy. But tube drivers are doing much better than you may think Commuters board a tube train at Victoria underground station in London ahead of strike action Photo: ANDY RAIN/EPA
